{"tid":1516661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一齊討論下鳩嗌成效！","createTime":"2019-08-29T15:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T15:51:56.000Z","uid":264174,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a36c92ae87903311154110821b998347955cb63e","tid":1516661,"uid":264174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:44:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">依家嗌到我啊媽開始習慣咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n話說個幾禮拜前開始嗌<br />\n嗰陣啊媽仲係咁叫我收聲唔好再嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話都冇其他人嗌 又話會比人投訴<br />\n但經過琴日啲人大聲到佢都聽到<br />\n然後今日就問點解冇人嗌既（9點嗰陣問）<br />\n我就笑住同佢講 因為未到十點囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就話乜定左嫁？<br />\n我話係嫁 我地有共識嫁<br />\n佢仲話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">做乜唔用大聲公嗌</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後我今日嗌足半個鐘佢都再冇理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實嗌嗌下啲人就會開始慣嫁啦<br />\n仲可能會影響到佢地嗌埋一份<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">手足們千祈唔好放棄啊！<br />\n每晚十點 準時窗邊見</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>831 遮打見 901 機場見</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2bb8b6bda53f71b0f91729a7680ac3dff37f2b7b","tid":1516661,"uid":231818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"b30fb52db7766f16393e46ab862b20e4d8eeff3b","tid":1516661,"uid":216390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:44:54.000Z","msg":"一日比一日多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慢慢感染屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32539519b58bce6aae08aef6928dca2bcc8985d5","tid":1516661,"uid":264174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b30fb52db7766f16393e46ab862b20e4d8eeff3b","tid":1516661,"uid":216390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:44:54.000Z","msg":"一日比一日多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慢慢感染屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:47:53.000Z","msg":"大家都行多一步就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aab25b2132dc15ad6c98fc06f3c84bdeff649ae","tid":1516661,"uid":105032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:50:23.000Z","msg":"可唔可以收台之前唱埋英國國歌？好似以前電視台咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cV3QdfNOewk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcV3QdfNOewk&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkLM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=500e63d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cV3QdfNOewk</a>"},{"pid":"241a61d6d80559a623bb324b9afaebc046dbce8c","tid":1516661,"uid":105032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aab25b2132dc15ad6c98fc06f3c84bdeff649ae","tid":1516661,"uid":105032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:50:23.000Z","msg":"可唔可以收台之前唱埋英國國歌？好似以前電視台咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.